                        p Completed July 2022 (pending assessment). The course covers all aspects of deigning a good User Experience. As with the Coding Practices course, it is Agile / Scrum centric. More information on the syllabus is available <a href="https://www.qualhub.co.uk/media/19898/603-7619-3-qualification-specification-version-10.pdf">HERE</a>.
