                        p Completed early April 2022, the course covered much more than just code, encompasing the entire development cycle. Oriented mostly around Scrum and other Agile methodologies. Included units on Test Driven Development, UI/UX, Deployment and much more. More information on the syllabus is available <a href="https://www.qualhub.co.uk/media/20704/603-5793-9-qualification-factsheet-version-10.pdf">HERE</a>.
